      <div class="explanation-box">
        <div class="box-label">📖 Chapter Overview</div>
        <p>Yeh chapter Accounting ki neenv hai. Isme hum seekhte hain ki Accounting kya hai, iski zaroorat kyun hai, aur kaun se Concepts aur Principles use karke accounts banaye jaate hain. Theory question aate hain — agar aap clearly yaad karo to ye easy marks hain!</p>
