      <div class="topics-grid">
        <div class="topic-item"><div class="ti-dot"></div>Meaning, Scope & Objectives of Accounting</div>
        <div class="topic-item"><div class="ti-dot"></div>Accounting Concepts & Conventions (12 types)</div>
        <div class="topic-item"><div class="ti-dot"></div>Capital vs Revenue Expenditure & Receipts</div>
        <div class="topic-item"><div class="ti-dot"></div>Contingent Assets & Contingent Liabilities</div>
        <div class="topic-item"><div class="ti-dot"></div>Accounting Policies (AS-1)</div>
