      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-title">🏆 GOLDEN RULES — Must Memorize</div>
        <span class="highlight">Personal A/c:</span>  Debit the Receiver | Credit the Giver<br>
        <span class="highlight">Real A/c:</span>      Debit what comes in | Credit what goes out<br>
        <span class="highlight">Nominal A/c:</span>   Debit all Expenses/Losses | Credit all Income/Gains<br><br>
        <span class="gold">Modern Approach (Alternative):</span><br>
        Assets ↑ → Debit | Assets ↓ → Credit<br>
        Liabilities ↑ → Credit | Liabilities ↓ → Debit<br>
        Income ↑ → Credit | Expenses ↑ → Debit
      </div>
