        Balance as per Cash Book (Dr / Favourable)        <span class="highlight">₹ XX,XXX</span><br>
        ADD: Cheques issued but not presented to bank      <span class="gold">+ ₹ XX</span><br>
        ADD: Direct deposits by customers in bank          <span class="gold">+ ₹ XX</span><br>
        LESS: Cheques deposited but not cleared            <span class="highlight">- ₹ XX</span><br>
        LESS: Bank charges debited by bank                 <span class="highlight">- ₹ XX</span><br>
        LESS: Direct payments by bank (standing orders)    <span class="highlight">- ₹ XX</span><br>
        ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br>
        <span class="gold">Balance as per Pass Book (should match)</span>    <span class="highlight">₹ XX,XXX</span>
      </div>
