      <div class="explanation-box">
        <div class="box-label">📖 Chapter Overview</div>
        <p>Inventory valuation mein hum closing stock ki value calculate karte hain. Yeh directly profit/loss ko affect karta hai — isliye ICAI ne ise AS-2 (Accounting Standard) se regulate kiya hai. FIFO aur Weighted Average Method sabse important hain.</p>
