      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-title">📐 KEY FORMULA</div>
        <span class="highlight">Closing Stock Value</span> = Lower of Cost or Net Realisable Value (NRV)<br><br>
        <span class="gold">NRV</span> = Estimated Selling Price − Estimated Costs to Complete &amp; Sell<br><br>
        <span class="highlight">Cost includes:</span> Purchase Price + Freight + Import Duties + Conversion Costs<br>
        <span class="highlight">Cost EXCLUDES:</span> Admin overheads, selling costs, abnormal wastage
