      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-title">📐 AVERAGE DUE DATE FORMULA</div>
        <span class="highlight">Step 1:</span> Select a Base Date (usually earliest due date)<br>
        <span class="highlight">Step 2:</span> Calculate Days from Base Date to each Due Date<br>
        <span class="highlight">Step 3:</span> Products = Amount × Days<br>
        <span class="gold">ADD Formula:</span><br>
        ADD = Base Date + (Total Products ÷ Total Amount) days<br><br>
        <span class="highlight">Red Ink Interest:</span> Jab due date base date se pehle ho → Interest ko opposite side mein likho (Red Ink)
