        <span class="highlight">BALANCE SHEET:</span><br>
        Liabilities Side: Capital + Net Profit − Drawings + Long-term Loans + Current Liabilities<br>
        Assets Side: Fixed Assets + Investments + Current Assets<br>
        <span class="gold">Assets MUST EQUAL Liabilities (Balancing check!)</span>
      </div>
