      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-title">📐 PROFIT CALCULATION FORMULA</div>
        <span class="highlight">Statement of Affairs Method:</span><br>
        Closing Capital = Closing Assets − Closing Liabilities<br>
        Opening Capital = Opening Assets − Opening Liabilities<br><br>
        <span class="gold">Profit = Closing Capital − Opening Capital + Drawings − Additional Capital Introduced</span><br><br>
        <span class="highlight">Total Sales (Debtors A/c):</span><br>
        Opening Debtors + Sales (Credit) = Cash Collected + Closing Debtors<br>
        ∴ Sales = Cash Collected + Closing Debtors − Opening Debtors
      </div>
